at."}, {"start": 581.16, "end": 583.16, "text": " That wraps up today's video, guys."}, {"start": 583.16, "end": 585.16, "text": " I appreciate you all for tuning in, as always."}, {"start": 585.16, "end": 587.16, "text": " It really means a lot."}, {"start": 587.16, "end": 589.16, "text": " It's really motivating to see that people are returning viewers."}, {"start": 589.16, "end": 591.16, "text": " People are liking, people are commenting."}, {"start": 591.16, "end": 593.16, "text": " I read every comment, and I'm really"}, {"start": 593.16, "end": 595.16, "text": " trying hard to give you guys what you want to see."}, {"start": 595.16, "end": 597.16, "text": " Today's approach did kind of fail with the merch stand,"}, {"start": 597.16, "end": 599.16, "text": " but we still had some funny clips."}, {"start": 599.16, "end": 601.16, "text": " I'm trying to get more creative so it's not just the same old same."}, {"start": 601.16, "end": 603.16, "text": " I'm going to do something with bodyguards"}, {"start": 603.16, "end": 605.16, "text": " or a big black guy."}, {"start": 605.16, "end": 607.16, "text": " Those are like the requested ones,"}, {"start": 607.16, "end": 609.16, "text": " so we're working on that behind the scenes."}, {"start": 609.16, "end": 611.16, "text": " Trying to give you guys what you want to see."}, {"start": 611.16, "end": 613.16, "text": " I do want to make two points before the video ends."}, {"start": 613.16, "end": 615.16, "text": " Point number one, real men don't resort to violence."}, {"start": 615.16, "end": 617.16, "text": " A wise guy told me that once in Walmart,"}, {"start": 617.16, "end": 619.16, "text": " and if you think about it, it's true,"}, {"start": 619.16, "end": 621.16, "text": " because if you knock me out, I get hurt,"}, {"start": 621.16, "end": 623.16, "text": " I don't get anything from it, and then you get in trouble,"}, {"start": 623.16, "end": 625.16, "text": " you don't get anything from it."}, {"start": 625.16, "